Ukraine Khartsyzsky Doubles Pipe Production, Izvestia Reports

-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 
2011-06-02T06:16:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/ukraine-khartsyzsky-doubles-pipe-production-izvestia-reports.html
VAT  Khartsyzsky Trubny Zavod (HRTR) , a
Ukrainian pipe maker owned by billionaire Rinat Akhmetov, more
than doubled production in the first five months of the year,
 Ekonomicheskie Izvestia  reported, citing a company official.  The company produced 247,000 metric tons of pipes from
January through May, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
 dkrasnolutsk@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Willy Morris at   wmorris@bloomberg.net  